<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَقَامًا مَّحْمُودًا}</span> ... مَقَامَ الشَّفَاعَةِ العُظْمَى لِفَصْلِ القَضَاءِ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
