<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلْطَانًا}</span> ... حُجَّةً، وَقُوَّةً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَزَهَقَ}</span> ... بَطَلَ، وَاضْمَحَلَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَهُوقًا}</span> ... لَا بَقَاءَ لَهُ، وَلَا ثَبَاتَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَأَى بِجَانِبِهِ}</span> ... تَبَاعَدَ عَنْ طَاعَةِ رَبِّهِ كِبْرًا، وَعِنَادًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
