<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَاكِلَتِهِ}</span> ... طَرِيقَتِهِ، وَمَا يَلِيقُ بِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظَهِيرًا}</span> ... مُعِينًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
